Year: 2003


The Swiss Goth Metal band Samael have developed a following in large part due to their innovative use of various musical styles. This performance film features two different full concerts including a 1996 show in Krakow, Poland, and a 2002 appearance at the Summer Breeze Festival. Also included are a trio of music videos, interview clips, and additional live performances.
